# Blog App

## Project Overview
Blog App is a full-stack web application that allows users to create, read, update, and delete blog posts with secure authentication and responsive user interface.

## Problem Statement
Traditional content sharing platforms often lack simplified personal publishing workflows and secure user-specific blog management. This application provides a secure and scalable blogging platform.

## Features
- User Registration
- Login Authentication
- JWT Authorization
- Create Blog Posts
- Read Blogs
- Edit Blogs
- Delete Blogs
- Protected Routes
- Responsive UI
- REST API Integration

## System Architecture
Frontend → API Layer → Backend → MongoDB Database

## Tech Stack

### Frontend
- React.js
- Vite
- Axios
- React Router
- CSS

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- Mongoose
- JWT
- bcrypt
- dotenv
- cors

